title: Week of Revelry
body:
Rito.... what is this? {{champion:24}} 

Jax Oriental translates to Eastern Jax (I think), I'm fairly certain it is also Pax Jax... The picture is also a big hint. 

I'm probably missing something big due to the fact that this is on the Brazil website, or that the Jax skin name and icon might be a placeholder but still...

~ EDIT: Turns out 'Jax Oriental' is Temple Jax, after digging around a bit. Ah well.

replies.body: It's fisherman jax, or whatever that skin is called.
